{"tid":1498181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[#Eye4HK Campaign] #Eye4HK x 823人鏈攻略","createTime":"2019-08-23T09:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T03:14:00.000Z","uid":177289,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"427b76a3165cdab991160318b1a8ef5de31aaff7","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"> Post 1: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491510</a><br />\nPost 2: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1492195\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1492195</a> <br />\nPost 3: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493145\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493145</a><br />\nPost 4: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496534\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496534</a><br />\n </span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3kZhxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3kZhxd.jpg&h=ccee21bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我地係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Eye For Hong Kong Campaign #Eye4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nEye4HK 已經令手遮右眼係外國人眼中，視為香港抗爭symbol ，尋日最高紀錄係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每10分鐘有1411 tweets</span></strong></span>，喺歐洲特別係波蘭反應熱烈，亦有歐洲議會議員帶頭參與；連泰國、越南、剛果（係啊非洲嘅剛果）都有好多人參與，香港人去咗邊啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本嘅tweet rate 仲高過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚 823 香港之路，將會係另一次connect 國際嘅機會。香港人話自己國際化，宜家成個campaign 同global 仲有好大段距離啊。跪求大家好似民間記者會咁，喺今晚823人鏈行動開始前，掩右眼三十秒，俾國際媒體影低呢個symbol 的一刻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHc5c9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHc5c9c.jpg&h=6abfa8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要令Eye4HK 一傳十十傳百，麻煩大家今晚post 完selfie，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TAG 至少5個朋友</span></span></strong>，尤其係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外國朋友</span></span></strong>，跟以下format tag人：<br />\n<br />\n&lt;Eye for HongKong Campaign&gt;<br />\n To show your support to Hong Kong, please join the &ldquo;Eye for HongKong Campaign&rdquo;: <br />\n<br />\n1. Take a selfie with your right eye covered. Consider wearing a mask, which symbolizes Hong Kong people&rsquo;s fear of expression, if you wish<br />\n2. Upload the photo to Facebook/Instagram/Twitter/Reddit <br />\n3. Tag at least 4 of your friends to take part in this challenge in the next 24 hours<br />\n@ @ @ @ <br />\n4. Add the following hashtag:<br />\n<br />\n#EyeforHK<br />\n#Eye4HK <br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK<br />\n<br />\n好多人只係forward 個campaign 文宣圖當做左，俾人tag 嘅又唔找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個campaign 唔需要眾籌，唔需要物資，連文宣都唔太需要，需要嘅係你親身參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明白前線會擔心安全問題，安全問題請參考返上個post嘅Q&amp;A。但！係！和理非同冷氣軍師唔好係度扮前線，求求大家，前線幫你擋子彈，宜家只係想你幫手做一次港女港男，自拍一張將Eye4HK tag 出國際，connect HK to the world，咁微小嘅訴求，你可唔可以唔好似香港政府咁零回應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead7b4a975c590c2031898d59389835ac5ca0ee7","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！"},{"pid":"6953552f757a474c6e2a2ff9002572a78188a3bd","tid":1498181,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"無力都推"},{"pid":"f89407cef39526278e057ea27063cc7882e3ca51","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>#EyeforHK<br />\n#Eye4HK <br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"029a4a6ba397c92d79e0e8d2ecd5c0aa9b5911e3","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:59:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>#EyeforHK<br />\n#Eye4HK <br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"0567499164b03331c411ca3e2c56ef2994f741d9","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>#EyeforHK<br />\n#Eye4HK <br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"273700364edf4cca0a2deb45310d8b85badc1da3","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>#EyeforHK<br />\n#Eye4HK <br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"126e1eb3b155f777148981210b6d33923d44509f","tid":1498181,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d65143f4e0686797d4ec993147c5dd6f7a72958","tid":1498181,"uid":177289,"like